				<div class="section-content">
					<div class="section-inner layoutSingleColumn">
						<h1 name="8483" id="8483" class="graf--h3 graf--leading graf--title">
							<strong class="markup--strong markup--h3-strong">Artist Interview: </strong>Ambrus Tövisházi<strong class="markup--strong markup--h3-strong">, Péterfy Bori &amp; Love&nbsp;Band</strong>
						</h1>
						<p name="1e78" id="1e78" class="graf--p graf-after--h3">
							<strong class="markup--strong markup--p-strong">
							<em class="markup--em markup--p-em">~QRATES speaks to the artist about his upcoming and recently funded project as well as the importance of remaining independent in the music industry~</em>
							</strong>
						</p>
						<p name="2afd" id="2afd" class="graf--p graf-after--p">We are delighted to have an interview with such a multi-talented artist Ambrus Tövisházi from Budapest, Hungary.</p>
						<p name="71c0" id="71c0" class="graf--p graf-after--p">He has been using our service QRATES since the start and his last successful project LP “<a href="https://qrates.com/artists/11016/items/11046" data-href="https://qrates.com/artists/11016/items/11046" class="markup--anchor markup--p-anchor" target="_blank">2B</a>” as Péterfy Bori &amp; Love Band was a great success. His latest project “<a href="https://qrates.com/artists/11016/items/11747" data-href="https://qrates.com/artists/11016/items/11747" class="markup--anchor markup--p-anchor" target="_blank">Szédülés</a>” is currently funding on QRATES now. To support his latest LP, which will be pressed on as a special 180 heavy vinyl, we have asked him about the story behind this LP as well as his favorite track on the album. It was interesting to find out about the music scene in Hungary, his love for vinyl and musical influences.</p>
						<p name="8ab9" id="8ab9" class="graf--p graf-after--p">
							<strong class="markup--strong markup--p-strong">Check out his music on his QRATES page </strong>
							<a href="https://qrates.com/artists/11016" data-href="https://qrates.com/artists/11016" class="markup--anchor markup--p-anchor" target="_blank">
								<strong class="markup--strong markup--p-strong">here</strong>
							</a>
						</p>
					</div>
